<br>
All I did was heal my pet when it got to 75% or so, bringing it back up to 100%, then going back to medding.  After a while PoD ran oom and did pure melee, so I stepped in to tank for my pet a few rounds since I had full health.  At about 5-7% he ran, then I unleashed HoE on him and down he went.  Afterwords I gave the robe and the staff to the lowbie chanter that watched me solo him <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br>
<br>
After the fight I had about 15% mana, and pet was at about 70% hp.<br>
<br>
